title: ValueError in examples/docker example
body:
### System information
- **Have I written custom code (as opposed to using a stock example script provided in MLflow)**: No
- **OS Platform and Distribution**: Linux Ubuntu 18.04
- **MLflow installed from (source or binary)**: source
- **MLflow version (run ``mlflow --version``)**: 0.9.1
- **Python version**: 3.7.3
- **npm version (if running the dev UI)**:
- **Exact command to reproduce**:
```
docker build -t mlflow-docker-example -f Dockerfile .
mlflow run examples/docker -P alpha=0.5
```

### Describe the problem
I am running the example at `example/docker` but I am getting an error after the experiment has finished
